      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "GOLDFlELD, New, March IS\nVery few Of the clerks of this place,\nafter having been given the alter\nnative of Withdrawing from the In\ndustrial Workers of the World or\nFORGETTING their positions, remained\nremained loyal to that body and all\nstores were reopened today. No\ndisturbances have occurred since\nthe killing of John Silva last week.\nMuch Ill feeling toward the Indus\ntrial Workers is entertained by the\nmembers of the Western federation.\nMiners of the Bull Frog, Manhat-\ntan, Seven Troughs and the Fair\nview have withdrawn."
    }
